						<summary>

						<p>This records the gift by three residents of Pullainallūr <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Vīrapāṇḍyanallūr of the incomes <hi rend="italic">uḷḷāyam</hi> and <hi rend="italic">paṭṭaḍaippadivu</hi> accruing to them from the village which was their <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> to the temple of Kaṇṇīśvaramuḍaiya-Nayiṉār.</p>						

